{"tid":2227822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9點半蘋果新聞報道初衷︱ 半小時消化每日大事 一家人睇冇拗撬","createTime":"2020-10-03T05:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T09:04:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee02f455b4ae3fbff7d7afb11d20428eb2f6395","tid":2227822,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201003/EXTVMR7OTFHXLEVBPDMEZLIZKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201003%2FEXTVMR7OTFHXLEVBPDMEZLIZKE%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=1341ba6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201003%2FEXTVMR7OTFHXLEVBPDMEZLIZKE%2F&h=1fa27d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201003/EXTVMR7OTFHXLEVBPDMEZLIZKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n9點半蘋果新聞報道初衷︱<br />\n半小時消化每日大事 一家人睇冇拗撬<br />\n<br />\n手機普及改變了大眾睇新聞方式，但我們相信仍有不少市民，依然依賴傳統電視的新聞報道，去消化每日圍繞身邊的大事。《9點半蘋果新聞報道》的誕生，正是為大家提供多一個渠道，讓大家花約莫半小時，便可知悉香港正在發生甚麼事。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：9點半蘋果新聞報道︱10月5日起 每晚9:30 報真相 講人話<br />\n<br />\n重拾一家人睇新聞報道的樂趣<br />\n<br />\n我們知道，當新聞媒體逐漸被染紅，一個能保持客觀、多角度、事事求真的新聞報道，在紛亂社會中，是不可或缺。我們深信，健康的新聞報道，能令人時刻保持獨立思考，清晰理解當前局勢。我們明白，全面的新聞報道，能減少家人因政見不同而產生的磨擦，重拾一家人睇新聞報道的樂趣。而這也是《9點半蘋果新聞報道》成立的初衷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IawvNufGrsMCPlfd7aK6h18BDZ8=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7MKG44GGBFBFNLZNLFDQO7GYMI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIawvNufGrsMCPlfd7aK6h18BDZ8%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7MKG44GGBFBFNLZNLFDQO7GYMI.png&h=f5b71fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家人因政見不同，隨時產生不必要磨擦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYouTube一個掣 駁電視齊齊睇<br />\n<br />\n接駁上電視的方法亦相當簡單，大家只要利用手機上的YouTube App播放《9點半蘋果新聞報道》，然後按右上方連接電視的圖案，便可瞬間投放至電視螢幕。若果觀眾沒有smart TV，亦可購買外置連接器，將新聞駁上電視。<br />\n<br />\n《9點半蘋果新聞報道》將於10月5日（星期一）晚上9點半正式首播，每晚9點半約定你，透過YouTube、Facebook或《蘋果動新聞》的果燃台一家人一齊收看獨家直播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MbJ3sAfXeJOlK5ZV9L4hT9iDnaM=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YNXQC6VWKJBENE42HER7QYITH4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMbJ3sAfXeJOlK5ZV9L4hT9iDnaM%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYNXQC6VWKJBENE42HER7QYITH4.png&h=a23b06e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家可利用手機上的YouTube App播放《9點半蘋果新聞報道》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e57omi6a_T0sER-1EvAXe9S_w4s=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYY5UHMFHRBDTJMESRDPX77BZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe57omi6a_T0sER-1EvAXe9S_w4s%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYY5UHMFHRBDTJMESRDPX77BZQ.png&h=493f91ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按右上方連接電視的圖案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FhX9n5JeYGuRo6Ytc6-1Oq43mik=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZYSRKIHEJNDO3IQELDE3KHNFI4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFhX9n5JeYGuRo6Ytc6-1Oq43mik%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZYSRKIHEJNDO3IQELDE3KHNFI4.png&h=86ad61f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瞬間投放至電視螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ue49LD0uQoTz3emgjqKRP7CvOLw=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LVDK3V4XRVBP5HN6DIZ2VB57GA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fue49LD0uQoTz3emgjqKRP7CvOLw%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLVDK3V4XRVBP5HN6DIZ2VB57GA.png&h=8c2047b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒有smart TV的話，亦可購買外置連接器，將新聞駁上電視。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LV6-aycCcZnCsngEcLELAWqLDKQ=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EIHHBU6PEFFYLGKGVCBEELKSHU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLV6-aycCcZnCsngEcLELAWqLDKQ%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEIHHBU6PEFFYLGKGVCBEELKSHU.png&h=08df1bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一家人睇新聞冇難度。"},{"pid":"dcf1a16f1f79fdbd7e02430ae84a1802957cb5b3","tid":2227822,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f6cb8c9afbad4e52a39af26b81d2283b159029","tid":2227822,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"今晚開始"},{"pid":"c387f889414e070cd35949467fd2bef5fa03a2ec","tid":2227822,"uid":114080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}